OL,5, Shops in France will be ordered to     
OL,6, close doors when using air conditioning
OL,7, and limit neon lighting in a bid to cut
OL,8, energy waste, a minister has said.     
OL,10,FThese rules, already in place in some  
OL,11,Fareas, will be rolled out across       
OL,12,FFrance, Minister of Ecological         
OL,13,FTransition Agnes Pannier-Runacher told 
OL,14,Fthe Journal du Dimanche newspaper.     
OL,16,FEnergy costs in Europe have spiralled  
OL,17,Fsince the Russian invasion of Ukraine. 
OL,19,FShops will be fined up to 750 euros    
OL,20,F(#640) for breaking the                
OL,21,Fair-conditioning rule.                 
